title: daggny_taggart
author: daggny_taggart
content: OUR MAIN CAMPAIGN is posted  here But we decided to have one more page for REDDIT as our Twitter campaign is now canceled. EVeryone who already registered can continue working    Website :: Whitepaper :: RedditTo Participate, please follow our Reddit channel then upvote and comment on all of our Reddit announcements there. This will get you a one-time 1 stake.To receive weekly stakes, please make posts about the Incubatex Mint Event and include a link to our Discord. Also comment all of our new posts daily.Stakes are awarded based on the number of upvotes and comments:20-40 upvotes: 3 stake40- 80: 5 stakes80 - 120: 8 stakes120 - 200: 10 stakes200+:12 stakesIf your post goes viral (1000+) you will get a special stake allocation and reward from our Bounty Fund.   Stakes will be rewarded monthly.  Weekly reporting must be done under this thread.Approved Bounty participants will find their usernames under the "View stakes" button above. Be sure to use the tabs at the bottom of the document to check specific Bounty Campaign lists.
